===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|еӨ§|еңӯ|c1=s|c2=p|ls=psc}}.

Originally, the phonetic component is not related to the concept of earth ([[еңҹ]]) since in its original form it represents a pair of ritual axes perhaps made of jade [[еЈ«]]. Hence, the link to the concept of earth in this character either comes from folk etymology or its appearance in the Small Seal script.

